<surface xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:mith="http://mith.umd.edu/sc/ns1#" ulx="0"
  uly="0" lrx="5410" lry="6872" xml:id="ox-ms_shelley_e2-0042" partOf="#ox-ms_shelley_e2" mith:folio="20v" mith:shelfmark="MS. Shelley e. 2">
  <graphic url="https://iiif.bodleian.ox.ac.uk/iiif/image/ebe2c6fa-169a-4429-b84b-25a807bc53a3"/>
  <zone type="main">
    <line>Earth can console, Heaven can torment no <add place="sublinear">more</add></line>
    <milestone unit="tei:speaker" spanTo="#e2-0042.02"/>
    <line rend="center">Panthea</line>
    <anchor xml:id="e2-0042.02"/>
    <line>Hast thou forgotten one who watch<retrace cause="unclear">es</retrace> thee</line>
    <line>The cold dark night, &amp; never sleeps but when</line>
    <line>The shadow of thy spirit<del rend="strikethrough">s</del> falls on her?</line>
    <milestone unit="tei:speaker" spanTo="#e2-0042.03"/>
    <line rend="center">Prometheus</line>
    <anchor xml:id="e2-0042.03"/>
    <line>I said all hope was vain but love—thou lovest...</line>
    <line><del rend="strikethrough">But the eastern star is pale</del></line>
    <milestone unit="tei:speaker" spanTo="#e2-0042.04"/>
    <line rend="center">Panthea</line>
    <anchor xml:id="e2-0042.04"/>
    <line><add place="superlinear">Deeply</add>In truth <del rend="strikethrough">most deeply</del>— but the Eastern star 
      <mod><del rend="strikethrough">is <add place="sublinear">pale</add></del><add place="superlinear">looks wan</add></mod></line>  
    <line>And Asia waits in that far Indian <mod>
        <del rend="overwritten">w</del>
        <add place="intralinear">v</add>
      </mod>ale</line>
    <line>The scene of her sad exile—<anchor xml:id="e2-0042.08"/><delSpan
        rend="strikethrough" spanTo="#e2-0042.09"/>tho her presence</line>
    <line>Makes fruits &amp; flowers &amp; sunwarm winds,<anchor xml:id="e2-0042.09"/>
      <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">&amp; sounds</del>
        <del rend="strikethrough"><add place="sublinear">smooth oer</add></del>
      </mod></line>
    <line rend="indent5"><milestone unit="tei:seg" spanTo="#e2-0042.10" corresp="#e2-0042.08"
        /><add>rugged once</add><anchor xml:id="e2-0042.10"/></line>
    <line>And desolate &amp; fro<retrace cause="unclear">zen</retrace> like this ravine;</line>
    <line>But now invested with fair flowers &amp; herbs</line>
    <line>And haunted by sweet air's &amp; sounds, which flow</line>
    <line>Among the woods &amp; waters: from the ether</line>
    <line>Of her transforming presence—which would fade</line>
    <line>If it were mingled not with thine—farewell</line>
    <line><add><metamark function="count">818.</metamark></add></line>
  </zone>
</surface>
